ion-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5d9b906f-1d64-41a8-bd20-2bd18c6e09d9\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-81338ab1-9836-4a76-b22f-409d80f6b0cd\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>디자인의 정의</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d0e3e993-5d13-4c18-930e-fa3a9cca60c1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6cd50630-406b-4c32-a05f-333086e2212f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-875e8d0a-2d68-4d4b-afdc-e848036bd9e3\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://namu.wiki/w/%EB%94%94%EC%9E%90%EC%9D%B8\" target=\"_blank\">https://namu.wiki/w/%EB%94%94%EC%9E%90%EC%9D%B8</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>  <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5e7fd9f5-2a9c-443f-83f0-bccafeb32272\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-43f8dd1d-f682-4bda-9290-63ed108df2cc\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-9f021a76-a80c-4469-9049-d9147040c941\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사전적인 의미의 디자인은 의상, 공업, 건축, 미술 각 분야에서 어떠한 목적을 가지고 만들어진 설계나 도안등의 통칭을 말합니다. 이에 따라 디자인은 시각디자인, 건축디자인, 의상디자인, 편집디자인등등으로 여러가지 종류로 나눠지고 그 범위 또한 넓다고 할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e55ccac1-5f28-462a-97de-ca1597da2548\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b3f5e7-fd50-4bb3-a5d2-8efe7e96f295\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://terms.naver.com/entry.naver?docId=1086152&amp;cid=40942&amp;categoryId=33074\" target=\"_blank\">https://terms.naver.com/entry.naver?docId=1086152&amp;cid=40942&amp;categoryId=33074</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>  <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-af7b7ff4-2976-4092-9ac6-21bedd5ccf22\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f4b8dc34-5389-4ebf-a1e7-54ee2fed7266\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-10321e82-2af4-449e-a2e8-a7044a3af12f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 참고문헌에서의 디자인은 크게 3가지로 나눕니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2543a487-b8a6-49e3-b95a-7a364bb9c419\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-decoration-unset\" id=\"SE-fd932437-3f2b-475d-92ae-b667986a485a\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ad24860e-89c6-422f-89de-4005617eb4bd\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset se-decoration-unset\" id=\"SE-6ba056f4-38eb-48a0-95ca-af655e7bc94f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link\" href=\"https://terms.naver.com/entry.naver?docId=1185315&amp;cid=33074&amp;categoryId=33074&amp;expCategoryId=33074\" target=\"_blank\">1. 시각디자인</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-34759385-db24-47f4-ba96-4f561cad3e72\" style=\"line-height:1.6923076923076923;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset se-decoration-unset\" id=\"SE-70d6811e-2198-44ce-9094-65ef6eeb2939\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset se-decoration-unset\" 